---
description: Mandatory session bootstrap and per-turn agent-context read contract
alwaysApply: true
---

On every new user message that requires substantive work, first read `/AGENTS.md`, then read its complete core per-turn set before any other tool or substantive response.

At the beginning of a new agent session, read `/BOOTSTRAP.md` and run the resolved `/scripts/bootstrap.sh` before project work.

Session-start reads do not satisfy later turns. A pure acknowledgment with no tools or project consequence is the only exception.
